  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Fabric.Admin/fabricLocations/{location}/edgeGateways":

      operationId: EdgeGateways_List

            subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every
            service call.

          required: true

            type: string

            Returns the list of all edge gateways at a certain location.:

        - description: Name of the resource group.

          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true

            type: string
          examples:

        - description: Location of the resource.

          name: location
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the list of all edge gateways at a certain location.:

        - description: Client API Version.
          in: query

          required: true

            type: string
            default: 2016-05-01

          in: query

          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string

          description: OK
          content:

              schema:

              examples:
                Returns the list of all edge gateways at a certain location.:

                    s_at_a_certain_location."

      tags:
        - EdgeGateways
      x-ms-odata: "#/components/schemas/EdgeGateway"
      x-ms-pageable:
        nextLinkName: nextLink

    get:
      description: Returns the requested edge gateway.
      operationId: EdgeGateways_Get
      parameters:
        - description: Subscription credentials that uniquely identify Microsoft Azure
            subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every

          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            default: 2016-05-01
          examples:
            Returns the requested edge gateway.:
              value: 2016-05-01
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:

              examples:

        - EdgeGateways
